title: Aquadirt Racer Pack
description: Pre-purchase LEGO® 2K Drive and get Aquadirt Racer pack. *Pre-purchase bonus offer available for LEGO 2K Drive Standard Edition until May 18 2023. Pack is included in the Awesome Edition and Awesome Rivals Editions. Terms apply.
longDescription: Pre-purchase LEGO® 2K Drive and get access to the Aquadirt Racer pack including a street car, off-road vehicle and boat. The Aquadirt Racer pack is included as part of the LEGO 2K Drive Awesome and Awesome Rivals Editions. *Pre-purchase bonus offer available for LEGO 2K Drive Standard Edition through May 18 2023. Offer is for the Aquadirt Racer pack which includes one (1) Aquadirt Racer Street Car, one (1) Aquadirt Racer Off-road Car and one (1) Aquadirt Racer Boat. The Aquadirt Racer Pack is included in the Awesome Edition and Awesome Rivals Editions. For digital pre-purchases, content will be automatically entitled in game . Terms apply.
